-- Suzlon Group's Order Book Is Currently at $5 Billion, Chairman Tanti Says
-- B y   R a k t e e m   K a t a k e y
-- 2010-11-15T06:35:00Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-15/suzlon-group-s-order-book-is-currently-at-5-billion-chairman-tanti-says.html
Suzlon Energy Ltd. and its units
have combined orders valued at $5 billion, Chairman Tulsi Tanti
said.  The wind-turbine maker is expanding into Chile, Argentina
and Mexico, Tanti said in an interview in New Delhi today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
